        "text": "; as opposed to the strangers from Judaea in the preceding verse. So ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Timothy 4:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", \"The time will come when they will not endure sound doctrine; but after their own lusts shall they heap to themselves teachers, having itching ears\" (see, as instances, ",
